{
  "stem": "3085.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, [LAUGHS] but that's where we were quartered, in, in those-- in, in, in those stables for about a week.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we didn't have-- I-- you know, I recall, for instance, as opposed to what happened in the ghetto, where we had sanitary facilities still-- in the-- in, in that gendarmerie station camp, we only had latrines.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And first-- my first experience with-- you know, as an 11-year-old boy-- with a latrine, wasn't a very pleasant one.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was a very different situation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I think all the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, what happened was that not just the Jews of Pecs, who were vacated-- evacuated from the ghetto ended up there, but also Jews that were rounded up from surrounding areas.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's how, actually, our family got united.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We got-- our-- my extended family on my mother's side all ended up in that same area so that we were actually together, some-- over a dozen, probably about 18 people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and we all-- that's where we met.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and we stuck together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in fact, we were deported together in the same cattle car.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in some sense, at-- you know, at that time, my mother was probably quite happy to see her mother and her sisters and, and other relatives at the same place.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was just, you know, fortuitous, in a way, that we all ended up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so about a week-- I think it was six days or seven days that we were in that-- under the control of the gendarmerie.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we were taken to-- back to-- sort of backtracking the town to the-- to the railway station, again walking.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were put in the cattle cars and deported.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
